00:02:14.366 --> 00:02:17.976
Three, two, one.

00:02:19.486 --> 00:02:21.696
In Asphalt 9, you focus on item

00:02:21.696 --> 00:02:23.366
and path selection with swipes,

00:02:23.936 --> 00:02:25.286
