To create cohesion and

00:37:01.716 --> 00:37:03.776
consistency between every aspect

00:37:03.776 --> 00:37:04.536
of your design.

00:37:05.816 --> 00:37:07.726
So your app or game also needs

00:37:07.726 --> 00:37:09.076
