00:37:24.446 --> 00:37:26.046
making it feel at home in the

00:37:26.046 --> 00:37:27.206
platform it runs on.

00:37:28.426 --> 00:37:30.006
Now I know it's really hard work

00:37:30.376 --> 00:37:32.766
to create designs that stick

00:37:32.836 --> 00:37:34.726
together, especially when it

00:37:34.756 --> 00:37:36.496
