design, it raises the overall

00:37:45.106 --> 00:37:46.436
quality of your experience.

00:37:47.186 --> 00:37:49.096
So to make your app or game

00:37:49.096 --> 00:37:51.416
cohesive, create a consistent

00:37:51.416 --> 00:37:52.296
design language.

00:37:53.316 --> 00:37:55.386
Lay out every single screen

00:37:55.386 --> 00:37:57.486
side-by-side and ask yourself,

00:37:58.076 --> 00:37:59.986
does anything feel out of place?

00:38:00.726 --> 00:38:02.076
And if it does, replace it with

00:38:02.076 --> 00:38:03.346
something that families better.

00:38:04.266 --> 00:38:05.886
And finally, cohesiveness

00:38:05.886 --> 00:38:08.046
applies to how your app or game

00:38:08.046 --> 00:38:09.136
runs on the platform.

